title: Dakine Anya Laptop Bag
description:
Check out 360° views of the 2012 Anya Laptop Bag in the Meadow print
Shoulder Bag Features:
- Interior fleece lined padded laptop sleeve
- Fits most 15” Laptops
- Zipper closure
- Vinyl trims and handles
- Adjustable and removeable cross body shoulder strap
- Metal hardware
- Interior zippered pocket
- Interior organizer pockets
- Nylon lining
